item.title: CVE-2023-0490|2024-08-02T05:10:56.413Z -- unknown -- f%28x%29%20toc
item.description: The f(x) TOC WordPress plugin through 1.1.0 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
